\id 1TI - Goofa 
\h 1 Ximotiyoosa 
\toc1 Phawuloosi Ximotiyoosas Xaafida Koyro Kiitaa 
\toc2 1 Ximotiyoosa 
\toc3 1Ximo 
\mt1 Phawuloosi Ximotiyoosas 
\mt2 Xaafida Koyro Kiitaa 
\imt1 Gaatha Qofaa 
\ip Ximotiyoosa geetettiya, ammaniyaa na7atethay, Guutha Iisiyan yelettis (Ha.O 16:1-3). Iya aayyaa Ayhude; iya aaway qassi Girike asi. I Phawuloosara issife ootheyssanne Wonggelaa ooson Phawuloosa matan maaddiya asi. Phawuloosi Ximotiyoosas xaafida koyro kiitay heedzu ayfe qofata minthi xeellees. 
\ip Ubbaafe koyrottidi kiitay, woosa keethan denddida worddo timirttiyabaa minthidi odees. Ha imatha timirttey Ayhude timirttiyafe baggaa, qassi Ayhude gidonna asaa timirttiyafe baggaa oykkis. Hessika, “Ha benttiya alamey nagaran iitida gisho asi atotethaa demmanaw dumma gidida xuura eranaw, issi issi kathata moonna agganawunne machcho ekkonna woykko azina gelonna agganaw koshshees” yaagiya qofaa baaso oothidi denddis. 
\ip Nam77antho qofay, woosa keetha aysobaanne goynno wogabaa tamaarssiya timirttiya, hessadakka woosa keetha kaaletheyssatinne entta maaddeyssati ay mela maara duusu daanaw bessiyako odees. 
\ip Wurssethan, Ximotiyoosi Yesuus Kiristtoosas oothiya lo77o asi waanidi gidanaw bessiyako, qassi dumma dumma ammaniyaa asaa matan iyaw de7iya aawatethay aybeekko, Phawuloosi iya zorida zoriya demmoos. 
\iot 1 Ximotiyoosa kiitaa ayfe qofata 
\io1 Gelo qofaa \ior 1:1-2\ior* 
\io1 Woosa keethi aysiya asaas imettida ayso wogaa \ior 1:3-3:16\ior* 
\io1 Ximotiyoosas imettida timirttiya \ior 4:1-6:21\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Nuna ashshiya Xoossaaninne nu ufayssan naagiya Yesuus Kiristtoosan kiitettida, Yesuus Kiristtoosa hawaare gidida, Phawuloosappe,  
\v 2 ammanon taw tuma na7a gidida Ximotiyoosas.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Ha.O 16:1\x* 
\p Xoossaa nu Aawa, nu Godaa Kiristtoosa aadho keehatethay, maarotethaynne sarotethay new gido. 
\s1 Worddo timirttiyafe naagetethi 
\p  
\v 3 Taani Maqedooniya bashe nena hadaridayssada, issi issi asati worddo timirttiya tamaarsseyssa digganaw ne Efesoonan gam77ana mela koyays.  
\v 4 Entti go77i baynna hayse odanne bantta kochcha taybuwa agganaada oda. Hessa melabay palama kaaletheesippe attin ammanon oosettiya Xoossaa oosuwas maaddenna.  
\v 5 Ha kiitaa huu7e qofay geeshsha wozanappe, lo77o kahappenne tuma ammanuwappe benttiya siiquwa denthethanaassa.  
\v 6 Issi issi asati hayssa aggidi, pathonna odakko simmidosona.  
\v 7 Entti Xoossaa higgiya asttamaare gidanaw koyoosona. Shin entti ay odiyakko woykko tuma oothidi odeyssi i aybeekko erokkona. 
\p  
\v 8 Asi besseyssada higgiyan go7ettiko higgey lo77o gideyssa eroos.  
\v 9 Issibaa akeekanaw koshshees. Higgey lo77o asaas medhettibeenna. Shin higgey, higge mentheyssata, worandzota, Xoosse yayyonnayssata, shemppo wodheyssata, nagaranchchota, geeshshatethi baynnayssata, tunata, hari attoshin bantta aayiw woykko aawa wodheyssata,  
\v 10 laammeyssata, addey addera laymateyssata, ase bayzeyssata, worddanchchota, worddon caaqqeyssata, woykko tuma timirttiyara gahettonna ay ooso ootheyssata seeranaw keyis.  
\v 11 He timirttey bonchchonne anjjettida Xoossay taani awaajjana mela taw hadara immida Wonggelaa giddon de7ees. 
\s1 Xoossaa maarotethaas Phawuloosi galatida galata 
\p  
\v 12 Taani oothiya oosuwan taw wolqqaa immida nu Godaa Kiristtoos Yesuusa galatays. Tana ba oosuwas shuumidi he oosuwas bessaasa gidi taybida gisho iya galatays.  
\v 13 Taani hayssafe kase iya cayeyssa, iya yedetheyssanne metootheyssa gidikkoka taani hessa eronnanne ammanonna oothida gisho Xoossay tana maaris.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Ha.O 8:3; 9:4-5\x* 
\v 14 Nu Goday ba aadho keehatethaa ta bolla gussidi, he aadho keehatethaara ammanonne siiqo Kiristtoos Yesuusa baggara taw immis. 
\p  
\v 15 “Kiristtoos Yesuusi nagaranchchota ashshanaw ha alamiya yis” giya qaalay ammantheyssanne asa ubbay ekkanaw besseyssa. Ubbaafe aadhdhida nagaranchchoy tana.  
\v 16 Shin merinaa de7uwa ekkanaw iya ammaniyaa asaas taani leemiso gidana mela Yesuus Kiristtoosi daro dandda7is. Taw ubbaafe aadhdhida nagaranchchuwas Xoossay ba maarota darssis.  
\v 17 Ayfen benttonnayssas, issi Xoossaas, hayqqonnayssas, merinaa Kawuwas, merinaappe merinaa gakkanaw galataynne bonchchoy gido. Amin77i. 
\p  
\v 18 Ximotiyoosa, ta na7aw, kase nebaa nabeti odida qaala bolla eqqada ha kiitaa hadara new immays. Ne he qaala kaalliko lo77o olaa olettana.  
\v 19 Ammanoynne lo77o kahi new de7o. Issoti issoti kaha dhayidi markkabey hobben dhayeyssada bantta ammanuwa dhayssidosona.  
\v 20 Hessa hanidayssata giddon Hemeneyoosinne Iskkinddirey de7oosona. Entti tamaaridi Xoossaa cayeyssa aggana mela taani Xalahes enttana aatha immas. 
\c 2  
\s1 Woosabaanne goynnobaa 
\p  
\v 1 Ubbaafe sinthatada, asa ubbaas Xoossaa oychchanaw, woossanaw, gaannatanawunne galatanaw besseyssa taani nena akeekisays.  
\v 2 Nuuni tuma ayyaana de7oninne geeshshatethan Xoossaa goynnishe sarotethaninne woppu gida de7on daana mela kawotasinne shuumata ubbaas woossite.  
\v 3 Hessa mela woosay nuna ashshiya Xoossaa sinthan lo77onne ufayssiyabaa.  
\v 4 Xoossay asi ubbay attanaadanne tumaa eranaada koyees.  
\v 5 Issi Xoossi de7ees. Xoossafenne asappe giddon gididi sigethiya issoy de7ees; ikka ase gidida Kiristtoos Yesuusa.  
\v 6 I asa ubbaa wozanaw bana aathi immis. Xoossay ba wodiyan asa ubbaa wozanaw koyeyssa bessiya markkay hayssa.  
\v 7 Xoossay tana Wonggelaas asttamaarenne hawaare oothidi dooriday hessassa. Taani tuma odays; worddotikke; ammanonne tumaa Ayhude gidonna asaas markkattana mela Xoossay tana shuumis.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt 2Ximo 1:11\x* 
\p  
\v 8 Hessa gisho, ubba bessan de7iya addeti, bantana Xoossaas dummayidi, hanqonne palama diggidi, bantta kushiya pude denthidi Xoossaa woossana mela koyays. 
\p  
\v 9 Hessada maccasay banttana haaridayssa qonccisiya, bonchchoynne maari de7iya ma7uwa ma77anaw bessees. Entti maari baynna huu7e dathan, worqqan woykko inqon, woykko al77o afilan banttana alleeqisoppo.\x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1Phexi 3:3\x* 
\v 10 Shin Xoossaas goynnays giya maccasay banttaw besseyssada lo77obaa oothona. 
\p  
\v 11 Maccasi kiitetethan si77i gidi tamaaro.  
\v 12 Taani maccasay tamaarssana mela woykko adde bolla aawatana mela gidonnashin si77i gidi daana mela koyays.  
\v 13 Addaamey koyro medhettis; guyeppe Hewaanna medhettasu.\x - \xo 2:13 \xt Medhe 2:7,21-22\x* 
\v 14 Qassi cimettada Xoossaa higgiya menthiday maccasippe attin Addaame gidenna.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt Medhe 3:1-6\x* 
\v 15 Shin maccasi ammanon, siiqoninne geeshshatethan banttana haaridi de7ikko\f + \fr 2:15 \fq banttana haaridi de7ikko: \ft Woykko iya yelida nayti ammanon, siiqoninne geeshshatethan banttana haaridi de7ikko.\f* nayta yelon attana. 
\c 3  
\s1 Woosa keethaa cimata 
\p  
\v 1 Oonikka, “Woosa keethi kaalethiya asi gidanaw koykko lo77obaa amottees” giya oday tuma.  
\v 2 Woosa keethaa kaalethiya asi borettonnayssa, issi machchi xalaali de7eyssa, maaran de7eyssa, bana haareyssa, besseyssada ootheyssa, imathe mookkeyssa, tamaarssanaw dandda7eyssa,\x - \xo 3:2 \xt Tito 1:6-9\x* 
\v 3 mathottonayssa, ooyettonayssa, palamonnayssa, miishe siiqonnayssa,  
\v 4 iya nayti iyaw kiitetteyssanne bonchcheyssa, ba keethaa aysanaw dandda7eyssa gidanaw bessees.  
\v 5 Issi asi ba keethaa aysanaw dandda7onnaa ixxiko, Xoossaa woosa keethi waati aysanaw dandda7ii? 
\p  
\v 6 Otoron sugettidi, Xalahey Xoossaa pirddan kunddidayssada kunddonna mela, oorathi ammanida asi gidanaw bessenna.  
\v 7 Boreninne Xalahe xihen gelonna mela he uray ammanonna asa matan nashetteyssa gidanaw bessees. 
\s1 Woosa keetha daaqoneta 
\p  
\v 8 Hessada qassi woosa keethaa daaqoneti bonchchettidayssata, nam77u doona odettonayssata, daro woyne ushshaa uyonnayssata, miishe yaaretonnayssata,  
\v 9 ammanuwa xuuraa geeshsha kahan naageyssata gidanaw bessees.  
\v 10 Entti koyrottidi paacettanaw koshshees; entta bolla borey baynna ixxiko, woosa keethaa daaqone gididi ootho. 
\p  
\v 11 Hessadakka, entta maccasati bonchchettidayssata, zigironnayssata, maaran de7eyssata, ubbaban ammanetteyssata gidanaw bessees. 
\p  
\v 12 Woosa keethaa daaqoneti issi machchi xalaali de7eyssa gido. Ba naytanne ba keethaa loythi ayseyssa gidanaw bessees.  
\v 13 Woosa keethaa daaqone gididi, lo77o ooso ootheyssati, enttaw gita bonchcho qassi Kiristtoos Yesuusan banttaw de7iya ammanuwabaa odanaw daro minotethi demmana. 
\s1 Gita xuuraa 
\p  
\v 14 Taani ha kiitaa new xaafashe, ellesada neekko baana gada ufayssi wothays.  
\v 15 Shin taani boonna gam77iko, Xoossaa Keethan asay waanidi daanaw bessiyako erana mela hayssa new xaafays. De7o Xoossaa keethay tumatethaas tuussinne baaso.  
\v 16 Nu ammanuwa xuuray sidhey baynna gita. 
\q1 Kiristtoosi asho ma77idi qonccis; 
\q2 Iya tumatethaa Geeshsha Ayyaanay markkattis. 
\q1 Kiitanchchotas benttis; 
\q2 I kawotetha ubbaas sabbakettis. 
\q1 Alamen de7iya asan ammanettis; 
\q2 bonchchon salo ekettis. 
\c 4  
\s1 Worddo asttamaareta 
\p  
\v 1 Yaana wodiyan balethiya ayyaanatanne tuna ayyaanata timirttiya kaallidi, issi issi asay ammanuwa kaddanayssa Geeshsha Ayyaanay qonccisidi odis.  
\v 2 Hessa mela timirttey entta kahay doccin, asaa balethiya worddanchcho asttamaaretappe yees. 
\p  
\v 3 Hessa mela asati ekonne gelo qassi issi issi kathata moonna mela diggoosona. Shin ammaneyssatinne tumaa ereyssati Xoossaa galati woossidi maana mela Xoossay kathi medhdhis.  
\v 4 Xoossay medhdhida ubbabay lo77o. Xoossaa galatidi miikko wora wodhdhiyabay aybikka baawa.  
\v 5 Ubbabay Xoossaa qaalaninne woosan geeshshi gidees. 
\s1 Kiristtoosas ammanettida aylle gido 
\p  
\v 6 Hessa gisho, neeni ha timirttiya ammaneyssata tamaarssiko, nu ammanuwaninne lo77o timirttiya kiitettada diccida Kiristtoos Yesuusa lo77o aylle gidana.  
\v 7 Shin go77i baynna tuma gidonna odappenne cima maccasaa haysiyappe baqata. Tuma ayyaana de7on daanaw nena loohisa.  
\v 8 Asi ba asatethaa minthanaw oothiya oosoy guuthi maaddees. Shin tuma ayyaana de7on bana loohisoy ha77ika merinawukka de7o immiya ufayssi de7iya gisho ubbaas maaddees.  
\v 9 Ha qaalay asa ubbay ekkanaw bessiya tuma oda.  
\v 10 Nuuni asa ubbaa, ubbaafe aathidi ammaneyssata ashshiya de7o Xoossaafe ekkana gidi ufayssan naagiya gisho, hessas nuuni ooson daaburosinne baaxetoos. 
\p  
\v 11 Hayssa kiittanne tamaarssa.  
\v 12 Neeni yalaga gidiya gisho nena oonikka kadhoppo. Shin ammaneyssatas neeni odan, ooson, siiqon, ammanoninne geeshshatethan leemiso gida.  
\v 13 Taani yaana gakkanaw asaas Geeshsha maxaafaa nabbabon, sabbakoninne tamaarsson minna.  
\v 14 Tinbbitey odettin, cimati bantta kushiya ne bolla wothida wode neeni ekkida, nenan de7iya Geeshsha Ayyaana imotaa kadhoppa. 
\p  
\v 15 Ne dichchay asa ubbaas qonccana mela hessa mintha qoppa; hayssa ubba wode ootha.  
\v 16 Ne huu7iyasinne ne timirttiyas naageeta. Neeni hessa ubba wode oothiko nenanne nena si7eyssata ashshaasa. 
\c 5  
\s1 Am77etabaa 
\p  
\v 1 Cima addeta ne aawada bonchchafe attin hanqettofa. Yalaga addeta ne ishada oothada xeella.  
\v 2 Cima maccasata ne aayida, yalaga maccasata ne michchida, polo geeshshatethan oykka. 
\p  
\v 3 Azini hayqqida tuma am77eta bonchcha.  
\v 4 Shin am77ees nayti woykko nayta nayti de7ikko, he nayti tuma ayyaana de7on de7eyssa bessanaw banttana yelidayssatanne, bantta wogga aayiwunne wogga aawa maaddidi kushe zaaro tamaaro. Hessi Xoossaa ufayssiyabaa. 
\p  
\v 5 Barkka de7iya tuma am77iya Xoossafe maade demmanaw ufayssan naagasu. Gallasinne qamma Xoossay bana maaddana mela woossawusunne oychchawusu.  
\v 6 Shin ha alamiyan lo77o duussaa xalaala koyaa am77iya paxa de7ashe hayqqidaaro.  
\v 7 Oonikka entta boronna mela ha kiitaa enttaw imma.  
\v 8 Shin ba dabbotas, ubbaafe aathidi ba soo asaas qopponna oonikka ba ammanuwa kaddidayssa; ammanonna asappeka aadhdhida iita. 
\p  
\v 9 Laythi usuppun tammu kumiboonna am77ee sunthaa mazggaban xaafoppa. Qassi hessa bolla iya ba azinaas ammanettidaaro gidanaw koshshees.  
\v 10 Nayta dishon, imathe mokon, geeshshata tohuwa meechchan, metootiya asaa maaden, lo77o ooso ubbaas bana aatha immidaaronne lo77o ooson erettidaaro gidanaw bessees. 
\p  
\v 11 Shin yalaga am77eta sunthaa mazggaban xaafoppa. Enttana azina gelo gelo giya asho amoy oykkiya wode Kiristtoosa aggana.  
\v 12 Entti koyro gelida qaala menthida gisho pirddettana.  
\v 13 Hessa bolla entti ooso dhayidi keethafe keethe yuuyana. Yuushsha xalaala gidonnashin zigirssaninne banttana gathonnaban gelidi bessonnabaa odettoosona.  
\v 14 Hessa gisho, nu morkketi nu bolla odettiya iitabaa demmonna mela yalaga am77eti azina gelidi, na7a yelidi, bantta keethaa aysana mela zorays.  
\v 15 Hayssafe kase guutha am77eti Xalahe kaallanaw guye simmidosona. 
\p  
\v 16 Issi ammaniyaa maccasees soo asaa giddon am77eti de7ikko iya entta maaddanaw bessees. Hessada oothiko, woosa keethaas toohoy kawuyees. He wode woosa keethay maade bessiya tuma am77eta maaddanaw dandda7ees. 
\p  
\v 17 Woosa keethi loythi heemmiya cimati, ubbaafe aathidi, qaala sabbakoninne tamaarsson daabureyssati dakko bonchcho ekkanaw bessees.  
\v 18 Geeshsha Maxaafay, “Wudumman kathaa yedhdhiya booraa doona qachchofa” hessadakka, “Oosanchchoy ba damooziya ekkanaw bessees”\x - \xo 5:18 \xt Zaare 25:4; Maato 10:10; Luuqa 10:7\x* yaagees. 
\p  
\v 19 Nam77u woykko heedzu markki baynna, woosa keetha cima mootiyabaa si7oppa.\x - \xo 5:19 \xt Zaare 17:6; 19:15\x* 
\v 20 Harati yayyana mela nagara oothiya oonakka asa ubbaa sinthan hanqetta. 
\p  
\v 21 Neeni asa som77o be7onna, issuwa issuwafe dummayonna ha kiitaa naagana mela Xoossaa, Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosanne doorettida kiitanchchota sinthan ta nena zorays.  
\v 22 Oodde bollaka ne kushiya wothada shuumanaw ellessoppa. Harata nagaran geloppa; nena geeshshatethan naaga. 
\p  
\v 23 Neeni ubba wode harggettiya gishonne ne ulo harggiya gisho haatha xalaala uyoppa; guutha woyne uya. 
\p  
\v 24 Issi issi asata nagaray qoncce; entta nagaray entta pirddanaw enttafe sinthe aadhdhees, shin harata nagaray guyeppe gam77idi qonccees.  
\v 25 Hessada, lo77o oosoykka qoncce; qoncconna ixxikokka geemmanaw dandda7enna. 
\c 6  
\s1 Aylletas imettida zore 
\p  
\v 1 Xoossaa sunthaynne nu timirttey cayettonna mela aylletethan de7eyssati banttana haariya godata bonchcho.  
\v 2 Ammaniya godati de7iya aylleti, entta godati enttaw isha gidiya gisho entta kadhoppo. Entta oosuwan maaddettiya godati, ammaneyssatanne dosettidayssata gidiya gisho entti kaseyssafe aathidi oothanaw bessees. 
\s1 Worddo timirttiyanne tuma duretethaa 
\p Neeni hayssa tamaarssanawunne entti oothana mela zoranaw bessees.  
\v 3 Oonikka dumma timirttiya tamaarssiyaba gidikko, nu Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosa tuma qaalaranne nu ammanuwa timirttiyara gahettenna.  
\v 4 He uray otoron sugetteesippe attin aykkoka erenna. Enttaw issi qofa bolla palamanawunne ooyettanaw iita amoy de7ees. Hessi qanaate, ooshshi, cashshe, iita sidhenne,  
\v 5 giigonna palamaa kaalethees. Qassi enttaw iita wozani de7ees; tumaakka balidosona; entti Xoossaa ammanoy duretethas oge gidi qoppoosona. 
\p  
\v 6 Shin taw de7iyabay gidana giya asas tuma ayyaana de7oy gita wodhe.  
\v 7 Nuuni ha alamiya aykkoka ehibookko; qassi iyappe aykkoka ekkidi bookko.  
\v 8 Nuus kathinne ma7oy de7ikko hessi gidana.  
\v 9 Shin duretethi koyeyssati paaceninne xihen geloosona. Qassi enttana duge dafiyanne dhayssiya eeyatethinne qohiya amon kunddoosona.  
\v 10 Miishe siiqoy iitatetha ubbaas pultto. Issoti issoti miishe amottishe ammanoppe balettidi daro meton banttana yeggidosona. 
\s1 Ximotiyoosas imettida zorenne kiita 
\p  
\v 11 Shin neno, Xoossaa asoo, hessafe baqata. Xillotethaa, Xoossaa daano, ammano, siiqo, dandda7anne ashkketethi kaalla.  
\v 12 Ammano baaxiya loytha baaxeta. Daro asaa sinthan ne markkattida ne ammanuwabaa, Xoossay nena iyaw xeegida merinaa de7uwa oykka.  
\v 13 Ubbaas de7o immiya Xoossaa sinthaninne, Phenxe Philaaxoosa sinthan lo77o markka markkattida Kiristtoos Yesuusa sinthan ta nena kiittays.\x - \xo 6:13 \xt Yoha 18:37\x* 
\v 14 Nu Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosi qonccana gakkanaw ha kiitaa balinne borey baynna naaga.  
\v 15 Ba xalaala ubbaa haariya bonchcho Xoossay, kawota kawoy, godata Goday, ba qoppida qamman Yesuus Kiristtoosa zaari kiittana.  
\v 16 Issi iya xalaali hayqqenna. Oonikka shiiqanaw dandda7onna poo7on de7ees. Oonikka iya be7ibeenna; qassi be7anawukka dandda7enna. Bonchchoynne merinaa wolqqay iyaw gido. Amin77i. 
\p  
\v 17 Ha alamiya dureti coo dhayaa shalon otorttonna melanne ceeqqonna mela oda. Nuus koshshiyabaa palahisidi immiya nuna anjjiya, dure Xoossan ammanettana mela entta kiitta.  
\v 18 Entti lo77o ooso oothanaada lo77o ooson duretanaada, keehatanne haratas shaakkeyssata gidana mela kiitta.  
\v 19 Hessi enttaw sinthas mino baaso gidiya gisho he wode entti tuma de7oy ay daaniyakko erana. 
\p  
\v 20 Ximotiyoosa, issi issi asay, “Eratethi” giya eeya palamappenne hada odappe baqata; new imettida hadaraa naaga.  
\v 21 Issoti issoti nuus eratethi de7ees yaagishe ammanuwa aggidosona. 
\p Xoossaa aadho keehatethay hintte ubbaara gido.